This class works as a configuration file for all the classes in the project, so as its attributes will be taken and used as they are specified here.

CSVtoOntology
In this class many methods are defined to fill up an owl ontology with the desired new classes, individuals or properties assertions following the structure of a structured file (for example .csv) that has been transformed in an object of the type List, which works like a table.
